data.title: Heroic Southport Lifeboat volunteers awarded Jubilee Medals for life saving work
data.meta_description: Volunteers from Southport Lifeboat have been thanked for their life-saving work by being presented with special Jubilee Medals.  Crew members who have served the charity for the past five years have also been honoured.  A Southport Lifeboat spokesperson said: “Members of our crew were delighted to receive their Jubilee Medals for contributions to lifesaving at the time of Her Majesty …
